# MangaTrack

App para **seguir manga**, **marcar favoritos**, **leer capítulos** y **recibir notificaciones**, con tiers Basic/Premium vía Stripe.

## Stack

- **Next.js 15** (App Router) — `src/app/`
- **Clerk** — autenticación (`src/middleware.ts`)
- **Prisma 6** + **Neon (PostgreSQL)** — `prisma/schema.prisma`, `src/lib/db.ts`
- **Stripe** — premium (`src/lib/stripe.ts`, webhooks)
- **Resend** — email (`src/lib/email.ts`)
- **Playwright** — E2E (`tests/`)
- **Tailwind v4** + **shadcn** — `src/components/ui/`

## Estructura

```
src/
  app/
    api/
      manga/           — search, [mangaId], bookmark(s)
      chapters/        — [chapterId]
      reading-history/
      notifications/
      stripe/          — checkout, portal, price-ids
      webhooks/        — clerk, stripe
      user/            — profile, preferences, delete
    dashboard/         — biblioteca usuario
    search/            — búsqueda
    manga/[mangaId]/   — detalle
    reader/[chapterId]/ — lector
    settings/
    sign-in/ sign-up/
  components/          — UI + manga + DevTools
  lib/                 — auth, db, stripe, email, validations
  middleware.ts        — Clerk: rutas públicas vs protegidas
prisma/
  schema.prisma
  cleanup-legacy-catalog.sql — drop tablas mangas/chapters si quedaron
```

## Tiers

- `BASIC` — bookmarks limitados (50)
- `PREMIUM` — bookmarks ilimitados (lógica en API bookmark)

